from app import app,db
from model import *
import csv

def main():
    data=open('books.csv')
    r=csv.reader(data)
    
    for i in r:
        s=hello(isbn=i[0],title=i[1],author=i[2],year=i[3])
        db.session.add(s)
    db.session.commit()

if __name__=='__main__':

        main()
